These are Puzzles for 7x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-1-1::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: azalea, daffodil, orchid
There are 3 different favourite colors: black, apricot, light-blue
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, vegafina, bluemaster
City: liverpool, boston, colone
3 different pets are kept: goat, rabbit, ferret
House: farmhouse, modern, gothic-revival
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: may, july, october
 1. the person traveling to colone is the bluemaster-smoker##1
 2. the bluemaster-smoker is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1
 3. the person who growsazalea is the vegafina-smoker##1
 4. the farmhouse house is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in may is the person traveling to boston##1
 6. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1
 7. the bluemaster-smoker is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
 8. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the person who growsazalea##1
 9. the person who likes apricot is the person who growsorchid##1
10. the person who likes black is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2      |    3     |
| Flower      | azalea  | daffodil   | orchid      |
| Color          | light-blue      | black     | apricot     |
| Cigar           | vegafina | bluemaster  | alhambra   |
| City   | boston   | colone     | liverpool  |
| Pet   | goat      | rabbit      | ferret      |
| House   | gothic-revival      | modern    | farmhouse   |
| Birthday         | may    | july | october |

