.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-1-2::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: fuchsia, brown, lavender
House: townhouse, palace, wooden
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: lily, azalea, poppy
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: august, september, february
There 3 different types of food: peach, cauliflower, lime
There are 3 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, almond-milk, milk
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, tiparillo, dannemann
 1. the person who's birthday is in september is in the middle##1
 2. the person who likes lavender is the person drinking soy-milk##1
 3. the tiparillo-smoker is in the middle##1
 4. the person who likes brown is the person eating lime##1
 5. the townhouse house is on the far left##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 7. the person drinking milk is on the far right##1
 8. the person who likes brown is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
 9. the dannemann-smoker is on the far left##1
10. the wooden house is the person eating peach##1
11. the palace house is on the left of the person who growslily##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |     3      |
| Color         | brown | lavender  | fuchsia     |
| House           | townhouse        | palace | wooden    |
| Flower   | azalea  | poppy    | lily    |
| Birthday   | february    | september    | august   |
| Food           | lime        | cauliflower    | peach        |
| Beverage         | almond-milk     | soy-milk  | milk     |
| Cigar     | dannemann         | tiparillo       | cain |

