.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-1-3::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: filmmaking, writing, puzzles
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, reggae, metal
There are 3 different favourite colors: red, blood-red, ivory
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: tennis, weightlifting, rowing
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, daisy, bellflower
House: wooden, modern, craftsman
3 different games are played: domino, backgammon, whist
 1. the person playing domino is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
 2. the person who's sport is rowing is on the far left##1
 3. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 4. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 5. the fan of classical is on the far right##1
 6. the person who's sport is rowing is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 7. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1
 8. the wooden house is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
 9. the craftsman house is on the right of the person who likes blood-red##1
10. the person who likes ivory is the craftsman house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3      |
| Hobby      | puzzles   | filmmaking         | writing |
| Music-Genre          | metal  | reggae        | classical    |
| Color           | red | blood-red  | ivory  |
| Sport   | rowing | tennis | weightlifting         |
| Flower   | daisy | balloon-flower       | bellflower        |
| House           | wooden       | modern        | craftsman       |
| Game     | whist       | domino  | backgammon       |

