.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-1-4::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  doctor, coach, journalist
There are 3 different favourite colors: chestnut, aquamarine, red
3 different games are played: billiard, mah-jongg, canasta
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: rock, house, dubstep
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, havana, alhambra
House: cape-cod, tower, colonial
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: zinnia, lily, azalea
 1. the tower house is the fan of dubstep##1
 2. the coach is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1
 3. the cape-cod house is in the middle##1
 4. the alhambra-smoker is the fan of rock##1
 5. the person playing billiard is the doctor##1
 6. the person who likes chestnut is in the middle##1
 7. the colonial house is the person who growslily##1
 8. the person playing billiard is on the far left##1
 9. the person playing mah-jongg is the person who growszinnia##1
10. the person who likes chestnut is on the left of the fan of rock##1
11. the havana-smoker is on the left of the person who likes aquamarine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |       2       |       3       |
| Job      | doctor       | journalist      | coach          |
| Color          | red       | chestnut       | aquamarine          |
| Game         | billiard   | mah-jongg         | canasta   |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep       | house       | rock         |
| Cigar           | vegafina         | havana           | alhambra          |
| House         | tower | cape-cod | colonial |
| Flower     | azalea         | zinnia          | lily       |

