.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-1-5::.
House: cape-cod, art-deco, ranch-style
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: september, april, february
There are 3 different favourite colors: aquamarine, orange, chestnut
3 different games are played: bridge, chess, go
The people have 3 different jobs:  fisherman, musician, accountant
The people use 3 different means of transport: ship, boat, roller
City: rome, paris, prague
 1. the person playing go is on the right of the person who likes chestnut##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in april is on the far right##1
 3. the accountant is the person who's birthday is in february##1
 4. the person playing chess is the cape-cod house##1
 5. the person playing bridge is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
 6. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person traveling to prague##1
 7. the person driving the ship is in the middle##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
 9. the ranch-style house is the musician##1
10. the ranch-style house is the person traveling to rome##1
11. the person who likes orange is on the far right##1
12. the person playing chess is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |      3       |
| House          | cape-cod       | art-deco   | ranch-style        |
| Birthday         | february  | september | april      |
| Color   | aquamarine         | chestnut        | orange |
| Game   | chess           | bridge      | go       |
| Job   | accountant      | fisherman    | musician       |
| Transport           | roller        | ship      | boat       |
| City         | prague | paris   | rome     |

