The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, aconite, sunflower
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, romance, scientific
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, game, alhambra
 1. the person who growsaconite is on the far right##1
 2. the person watching scientific movies is the game-smoker##1
 3. the person playing go is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
 4. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the blend-smoker##1
 5. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person traveling to nizza##1
 6. the blend-smoker is the art-deco house##1
 7. the person playing mah-jongg is the person who growssunflower##1
 8. the futuristic house is the person playing mah-jongg##1
 9. the futuristic house is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1
10. the alhambra-smoker is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
11. the person traveling to nizza is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |        3        |
