.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-1-17::.
House: gothic-revival, craftsman, tower
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, ship, boat
3 different games are played: poker, monopoly, domino
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: marigold, sunflower, zinnia
3 different pets are kept: dog, pony, snake
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: march, april, january
There are 3 different favourite colors: emerald, chestnut, white
 1. the person playing domino is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
 2. the person who growssunflower is the person driving the airplane##1
 3. the tower house is the person driving the airplane##1
 4. the person who likes emerald is the owner of the pony##1
 5. the owner of the pony is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
 6. the person playing monopoly is the owner of the snake##1
 7. the person who likes chestnut is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in january is in the middle##1
 9. the owner of the snake is on the left of the craftsman house##1
10. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
11. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |        2        |       3        |
| House      | tower   | gothic-revival        | craftsman           |
| Transport         | airplane | boat          | ship      |
| Game           | poker   | monopoly | domino |
| Flower   | sunflower  | marigold       | zinnia         |
| Pet   | pony    | snake          | dog        |
| Birthday   | april  | january        | march     |
| Color         | emerald   | white         | chestnut       |

