There are 3 different favourite colors: lilac, blood-red, yellow
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: rose, zinnia, lily
There are 3 different nationalities: australian, brazilian, polish
House: art-deco, ranch-style, wooden
3 different games are played: bridge, billiard, mah-jongg
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: rock, dubstep, country
 1. the fan of dubstep is the person who growszinnia##1
 2. the person playing billiard is the person who growszinnia##1
 3. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
 4. the person who likes lilac is on the far right##1
 5. the person playing billiard is on the right of the fan of country##1
 6. the person who growslily is the owner of the chinchilla##1
 7. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the person who growsrose##1
 8. the art-deco house is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
 9. the australian is on the right of the person who likes blood-red##1
10. the owner of the turtle is the wooden house##1
11. the australian is on the left of the fan of rock##1
12. the polish is on the left of the person who likes yellow##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2      |      3      |
| Pet      | chinchilla       | rabbit      | turtle      |
| Color          | blood-red        | yellow | lilac   |
| Flower         | lily       | zinnia    | rose  |
| Nationality           | polish | australian     | brazilian    |
| House   | art-deco       | ranch-style   | wooden |
