.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-1-19::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: lilac, light-blue, grey
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, bellflower, daisy
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, bongani, bluemaster
City: liverpool, nizza, berlin
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: august, april, may
The people have 3 different hobbies: card-games, woodworking, photography
The people use 3 different means of transport: skateboard, jet-ski, car
 1. the person driving the skateboard is on the far right##1
 2. the person who likes grey is in the middle##1
 3. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the bongani-smoker##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1
 5. the person driving the car is on the far left##1
 6. the person who growsbellflower is on the far left##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in may is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person who likes lilac##1
 9. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the bolivar-smoker##1
10. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |      3      |
| Color      | light-blue      | grey         | lilac |
| Flower          | bellflower | daisy        | balloon-flower   |
