3 different games are played: monopoly, scrabble, whist
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daffodil, tulip, zinnia
There are 3 different favourite colors: coral, brown, fuchsia
House: modern, craftsman, palace
 1. the palace house is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1
 2. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the oliveros-smoker##1
 3. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the oliveros-smoker##1
 4. the baccarat-smoker is on the left of the person playing whist##1
 5. the person who growstulip is on the right of the person who likes fuchsia##1
 6. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the person who likes coral##1
 7. the craftsman house is the person who likes coral##1
 8. the oliveros-smoker is on the left of the person who growstulip##1
 9. the person who growszinnia is in the middle##1
10. the palace house is in the middle##1
11. the person who's sport is tennis is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
