| City      | liverpool       | london     | prague         |
| Cigar          | baccarat      | oliveros  | blend     |
| Sport         | tennis | ice-hockey     | snowboarding |
| Game   | monopoly  | whist | scrabble     |
| Flower   | daffodil    | zinnia      | tulip     |
| Color   | brown  | fuchsia    | coral  |
